com.magnitude.app
Class MagnitudeActivity

java.lang.Object
  Activity
      com.magnitude.app.MagnitudeActivity

public class MagnitudeActivity
extends Activity

MagnitudeActivity is the main class of Magnitude client application. It should be extended but source code is accessible as Magnitude.
is completely open-source. Some of the work of Chris Haseman has been used and improved in order to build this classes.

Author:
Magnitude client
